    "response_summary": "The response provides sorting and filtering options for reviews of a hotel with a total of 14,183 reviews. You can sort the reviews by \"Most relevant,\" \"Newest first,\" or \"Oldest first.\" \n\nFor filtering, there are several options available. You can filter by customer type, with 5,798 reviews from couples, 4,824 from families, and 1,934 from groups of friends. Additionally, you can filter reviews by language, including options like American English (384 reviews), Deutsch (7,952 reviews), and Eesti (21 reviews). There is also an option to filter by the time of year, such as March-May, June-August, or September-November, though currently, these filters show no available reviews. \n\nThe hotel in question has the ID \"1377073,\" and the filters and sorting tools are designed to help users navigate through the large number of reviews efficiently.",
